---
title: Sesame-Soy Beef Bowls with Sriracha Mayo, Cilantro & Wonton Strips
description: Bowls are way past “having a moment”—they’ve become a pillar of our lunches and dinners. Why? It’s simple: Everything’s better in a bowl! (Nice knowing you, plates.) But seriously, the customizable combo of carbs, protein, veggies, and a drizzle of delicious sauce cannot be denied. True to form, this rendition is fully-loaded. Buttery, lime-laced jasmine rice is topped with saucy ground pork and tender carrots. It’s all drizzled with a delectable Sriracha mayo, then topped with crispy wonton strips and fresh cilantro. One bite will have you totally bowled over.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66703c2598f15bd5272cf969-81947d8b.jpeg
